&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( tr . magnificent ) is an indian romantic-comedy film , directed by vikas bahl and produced by anurag kashyap and vikramaditya motwane . it stars alia bhatt and shahid kapoor in lead roles , with pankaj kapur and sanjay kapoor in supporting roles . the times of india described &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; as " india 's first destination wedding film " . principal photography began in august 2014 in leeds , and the film released on 22 october 2015 .